814
01:22:51,360 --> 01:22:55,069
Good evening, darling.
My name is Bond. James Bond.

815
01:22:56,160 --> 01:22:58,151
You know.

816
01:23:04,320 --> 01:23:07,198
Aren't you going to do something... funny?

817
