824
01:23:40,960 --> 01:23:42,996
Good evening. My name's Bond.

825
01:23:43,560 --> 01:23:45,471
James Bond.

826
01:23:53,160 --> 01:23:55,276
My God, but you're lovely.

827
01:24:09,720 --> 01:24:11,711
That was great!

828
01:24:11,840 --> 01:24:13,831
Genius.

829
01:24:43,280 --> 01:24:45,840
We meet again. I knew you wouldn't give up.

830
01:24:45,960 --> 01:24:50,795
