861
01:28:12,160 --> 01:28:14,355
I think.

862
01:28:27,040 --> 01:28:29,270
All right, lads, give her some air.

863
01:28:31,160 --> 01:28:33,549
Oh, we're fine, thank you.

864
01:28:33,680 --> 01:28:37,593
- How d'you feel third time around?
- Ecstatic, absolutely thrilling.

865
01:28:42,560 --> 01:28:44,596
