- No.

873
01:29:20,600 --> 01:29:22,670
My big scene is coming up.

874
01:29:23,600 --> 01:29:25,556
Not any more.

875
01:29:33,360 --> 01:29:36,750
Fine. You do it. Ciao.

876
01:29:53,240 --> 01:29:55,913
- Yes.
- <i>Is that my Peter?</i>

877
01:29:57,200 --> 01:29:59,953
Hello, Peg. What's the news from the front?

878
01:30:01,440 --> 01:30:03,476
