they can claim they saved your life.

884
01:30:23,120 --> 01:30:25,918
<i>Come home, love. I need to see you</i>.

885
01:30:27,760 --> 01:30:29,671
Nonsense, Peg.

886
01:30:29,800 --> 01:30:33,509
All you need is a wash and brush-up
and you'll be as good as new.

887
01:30:34,640 --> 01:30:37,154
No, it's not like that. Listen...

888
01:30:38,440 --> 01:30:40,476
Just a minute.

889
01:30:41,440 --> 01:30:44,000
Your boy's needed, Peg. You understand.

890
01:30:44,120 --> 01:30:46,111
I'm a star now.

891
01:30:46,240 --> 01:30:48,549
These people can't do a thing without me.

892
01:30:49,320 --> 01:30:51,515
It's everything you ever wanted.

893
01:30:53,600 --> 01:30:55,636
I love you, Peter.

894
01:31:00,800 --> 01:31:03,473
I'll see you soon. We'll go to tea.

895
01:31:05,760 --> 01:31:07,352
<i>Peter?</i>

896
01:31:39,760 --> 01:31:42,274
See how strong he was.

897
01:31:47,720 --> 01:31:51,030
