"I love you, Peter."

898
01:31:51,160 --> 01:31:53,196
But not my son.

899
01:32:01,800 --> 01:32:04,155
He came through like a champion.

900
01:32:11,280 --> 01:32:14,158
A star has an obligation to himself.

901
01:32:15,640 --> 01:32:17,710
Family weighs you down.

902
01:32:21,320 --> 01:32:25,154
