about this man a great deal.

937
01:38:04,000 --> 01:38:05,638
About how sad he is?

938
01:38:05,760 --> 01:38:08,991
No, about how marvellous his life must be.

939
01:38:09,120 --> 01:38:11,953
He has no future, no past, no responsibilities.

940
01:38:12,640 --> 01:38:15,677
He's simple, boring, an absolute blank.

941
01:38:15,800 --> 01:38:19,349
People expect nothing from him
and love it when they get just that.

942
01:38:21,240 --> 01:38:23,435
This is going to be my next film.

943
01:38:23,560 --> 01:38:27,314
- Are you absolutely sure about that?
- Absolutely.

944
01:38:28,320 --> 01:38:31,551
Cos you do have a choice, you know.

945
01:38:34,040 --> 01:38:38,272
- Have you read it?
- I've made some notes.

946
01:38:39,200 --> 01:38:41,350
I think it could be very funny.

947
01:38:41,960 --> 01:38:44,679
I don't like choice, Maurice.

948
01:38:44,800 --> 01:38:45,596
