957
01:39:19,240 --> 01:39:21,151
My heart's been troubling me.

958
01:39:21,280 --> 01:39:24,033
And I think, I think my mind...

959
01:39:25,320 --> 01:39:27,436
Peg's here.

960
01:39:27,560 --> 01:39:29,755
She's always with you, Peter.

961
01:39:29,880 --> 01:39:31,950
Now I've had a look at your heart

962
