967
01:39:47,880 --> 01:39:49,916
Do another Pink Panther.

968
01:39:51,240 --> 01:39:54,152
Are you sure, Peg? Are you really sure?

969
01:39:56,360 --> 01:39:58,510
Lt'll be a huge hit.

970
01:39:59,240 --> 01:40:03,119
And that'll give you the power
to make Being There.

971
01:40:20,480 --> 01:40:24,029
