its box-office potential as limited.

973
01:40:31,440 --> 01:40:34,318
Then I suppose this comes
at just the right time.

974
01:40:36,720 --> 01:40:38,472
I could never be this broke.

975
01:40:40,920 --> 01:40:43,434
